💀🎮Game Time🎮💀
------------------------
Being at The Lost Academy, caring for The Lost Student’s mental health is a priority. When they are on breaks or back to their dorm they often hang out at common places to read, study, ... or play game together. Anything that help them relax, have fun and distracted them from stress is fully supported by the academy.
The Lost Soul Kingdom links with “the awakened world” and most things were created by the subconscious mind of all the lost souls within it. That is why these things like game controllers, technology, ... that exist in The Lost Soul Kingdom are similar to those that exist in “the awakened world”.
-To be continued-
-Art Process footage available on Youtube-
------------------------
Hello my skeleton army 💀⚔️🖤,
I hope you enjoy the art of The Lost Academy so far! I really love and care for the lost students, they have been through a lot in “the awakened world”. They are so precious and I want to put them in scenery where they can have fun and relax. 
Also, thank you for your comments last time about things you do during school break, all your comments really bring me back to old days! It's so fun to read your side of the story and what you guys do back in school.
🖤Interact with me in the comment section: do you play game? And what game do you play🎮?
As for me, the game that I play most now is properly Chess♟, I also just remember, I sometimes also play Killer 13 card game (Vietnamese version) with my bf.
Can’t wait to read your answer 🖤💀🖤
Much love to you, my skeleton army!

💀Drinks Vending Manchine Break💀
Another scenery of the students of The Lost Academy. They are taking a break with their skeleton drinks (I lowkey want some).
Further more about The Lost Academy students. As their arrival at the academy, they would be separated into group of 4; one member from each House of The Lost Soul Kingdom: the students of The Curious Hunters, The Good Witches, The Chill Reapers and The coffin Makers. 
When they are awake in “the awakened world”, they would be studying subjects like Math, Literature, History, Science, ... and while they are in The Lost Soul Kingdom, The Lost Academy subjects, assignments and missions would focus more on sociology, psychology, mental health, art for therapy, etc.
Using the knowledge and power of their own house, they would be able to help each other going through their everyday challenge in “the awakened world” life.

-To be continued-
-See process video on my Youtube Vlogs-
----------------------------------
Hello my skeleton army 💀👑,
Thank you so much for all your comments in my last post. I love to read who you are as a “student”. I am also so happy to see many of you are interested in living in The Lost Soul Kingdom and want to enroll in The Lost Academy like I do! I think my school life there would be in peace everyday even though The Lost Academy’s subject can be very heavy and painful sometimes since every subject is about our real life situations (good and bad). But with friends and professors who would always be there to care for our life and help us out with exactly what we need to make our life be better would be so amazing. Therapy everyday!
🖤💀Interact with me in the comment section, when you have a break at school, what do you normally do? As for me and my favorite thing to do during breaks is to find my best friend in another class and would go play basketball together (highschool days).
I can't wait to come back and read your comments!
Take care, my dear Skeleton army 💀⚔️✨

⚔️💀☾Animal Constellation Observatory☾💀⚔️
--------------------
Exist in The Lost Soul Kingdom is The Lost Academy. The students are called The Lost Students, pronounce “they/them“ or by their House for example “The Good Witches Student“ or “Student of The Good Witches House“. The word “lost“ in their name does not necessarily means “lost their mind“ nor being miserable. They are here in The Lost Academy because they want to be curious, they want to be healed, they want to express or simply just being free.
-To be continued-
-See process video on my Youtube Vlogs-
----------------------------
Hello my skeleton army 💀⚔️,
I am back to posting more art this month. I am so excited to begin this new series called The Lost Academy. Like the Lost Soul Kingdom, The Lost Academy has it own unique stories. Even though I didn't aim for it, subconsciouly I was inspired by Harry Potter growing up (I watched it a thousand times already), I have always been inspired by the “school environment” like Hogwarts and places in the wizard world, like Diagon alley. However, my art always mean more personal to my life, philosophy and wisdom; not about the wizards 🥺 so you will need to see The Lost Academy in my perspective💀. Because of that this series of illustration will properly show you my subconcious mind, feelings and imagination in a perspective of “Student Kiv Bui”.
